Test dataÂ¶

Test data const objects are smaller datasets designed to be used in tests for other packages. They include 500 rows of data and include both Date objects and DateTime objects. All but one of the objects has an empty TimeArray meta field.

const Description
op single column Date data
cl single column Date data
ohlc four-column Date data
sdata single column DateTime data
mdata single column Date data with meta field
